{
  "texts": [
    "The details of setup is given in Appendix B.2.",
    "We first employ the widely used Huggingface Open LLM Leaderboard and AlpacaEval 2 as our evaluation benchmarks.",
    "Table 1 compares the performance of InfoPO against other preference optimization methods.",
    "Our results demonstrate that InfoPO is remarkably effective in improving performance.",
    "The average improvements over the best baseline are particularly notable in the Math domain, with relative gains exceeding 12% on Mistral and 3.5% on Llama3."
  ]
}